<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-79] Synapse does not lookup in a remote registry when full registry based configuration is given</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-79</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed the following issue when using full registry based configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-Specify the following in synapse.xml&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;synapse xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;!-- a full registry based configuration --&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     &amp;lt;registry provider=&quot;org.apache.synapse.registry.url.SimpleURLRegistry&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;root&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;file:repository/conf/sample/resources&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;file:repository/conf/sample/resources&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;parameter name=&quot;cachableDuration&quot;&amp;gt;15000&amp;lt;/parameter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/registry&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;/synapse&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-Place a synapse configuration file in ..repository/conf/sample/resources and define log mediator in it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Send a request through synapse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;messages did not go through the remote registry. Instead it invoked default main sequence which just sent message to endpoint.&lt;/p&gt;


</description>
